A '''New Republic case officer''' was an agent that was assigned to liaise with local resistance groups that were working against [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces on occupied [[Planet/Legends|worlds]].

==History==
[[Winter Celchu|Winter]] was the New Republic case officer assigned to the planet of [[Cilpar]] in [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]]. Her duties included supplying the local resistance group with weapons and vehicles, and coordinating them with [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] forces such as [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]].

{{Nr-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The title of case officer as presented in-universe is very similar to that of the [[Wikipedia:Central Intelligence Agency|Central Intelligence Agency]] and other real-world intelligence networks.

